    {
      "id": "key-diff-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1135,
      "y": 800,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "Key Differences\n\nTier 1 (Management):\n  AKS-MCP + UAMI\n  Cross-cluster access\n  Event Hub ingestion\n  Agent routing table\n\nTier 2 (Worker):\n  kagent-tool-server\n  Local RBAC only\n  Direct K8s watch\n  NS name → agent match",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "key-diff-box",
      "originalText": "Key Differences\n\nTier 1 (Management):\n  AKS-MCP + UAMI\n  Cross-cluster access\n  Event Hub ingestion\n  Agent routing table\n\nTier 2 (Worker):\n  kagent-tool-server\n  Local RBAC only\n  Direct K8s watch\n  NS name → agent match",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
